---
title: Honey-Soy Beef & Garlic Rice Bowl with Crispy Shallots & Sesame Slaw
description: Here's a recipe for success: take a bowl of garlic rice, add colourful pan-fried veggies and tender chunks of beef in a sublime honey-soy sauce and finish things off with creamy aioli and a smattering of crispy shallots.
